## High Level Picture

```
You manually copy token from Swagger
            ↓
Paste it when triggering GitHub Actions
            ↓
GitHub Actions passes it as env variable
            ↓
Test reads token from env variable
            ↓
RestAssured fires real request to hosted API
with Bearer token in header
            ↓
Captures actual response
            ↓
Compares with expected-response.json
            ↓
PASS / FAIL → report published
```

---

